@mcwhopper63 Hello, 
For transit passengers, entering Korea is not possible yet.

For more information, please contact to immigration center.

@Sophia_3110 Hi, Sophia.
Regarding pet in cabin service, Please find your reservation online under [MY &gt; My Trips] and book pets at [Additional Service &gt; Pets].
You can book pets up to 72 hours before all domestic and international flight operated by Korean Air.

@MauDominguez_ Dear Customer, thank you for choosing Korean Air.

If you mean that you want to book a seat through the agency with their award policy, please confirm your  reservation through them.
